  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Cleaned the issue, removing what was done.\n\nFor reference at the time of this comment, this is done:\n- [x] #245 documentation: warn to not use too many hierarchical levels for UX\n- [x] #395 documentation: add usage to slider\n- [x] #396 documentation: check usages of all widgets\n- [x] #491 documentation: update widget jsdoc on release.sh\n- [x] #472 documentation: unusable on mobile\n- [x] #473 documentation: missing default values in jsdoc\n- [x] #498 documentation: back button is not working\n- [x] #505  documentation: priceRanges example has two \"View HTML\" buttons\n- [x] #507 documentation: rendering of hierarchicalMenu is not correctly indented\n- [x] #499 bug: no error when instantiating an unkown widget\n- [x] #500 bug: css classes are doubled in pagination\n- [x] #502 documentation: add note on automatic rangeSlider min max computation\n- [x] #503 documentation/bug: css debug do not highlight label tag of checkbox\n- [x] #520 documentation/bug: menu text overlaps main text\n- [x] #522 documentation: slider not displaying well in airbnb example\n- [x] #524 documentation: glitch when menu over white background\n- [x] #528 documentation: the Template part of the page is cut\n- [x] #156 documentation: add algolia requirements for every widget\n- [x] #590 rename facetName to attributeName\n- [x] #563 new widget: numericSelector\n- [x] #488 `<script>` jQuery custom widget boilerplate\n- [x] #585 hierarchicalMenu: limit not working\n- [x] #504  documentation: Empty hitsPerPageSelector default value\n- [x] #575 widget.init interface not consistent with widget.render\n- [x] #558 new widget: starsList\n- [x] #485 rename indexSelector to sortBySelector\n- [x] #573 version not showing\n- [x] Put the link to the https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/ website\n- [x] Remove any mention to BETA/ALPHA, still ask for feedback of course\n- [x] #489 commonJS React custom widget boilerplate\n- [x] unpublish instantsearch.algolia.com website (ask @adam?)\n- [x] #493 documentation: link to the jquery, plain JS and react boilerplates in custom widget doc\n- [x] #576 manually test website and dev examples on mobile devices and supported browsers\n- [x] #577 examples should work and render good on mobile\n- [x] fix https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/pull/641/files commit\n- [x] /examples/ still have lorem ipsum showing\n\n~~#548 documentation: use specific version of instantsearch.js from jsdelivr~~\n",
    "created_at": "2015-11-12T15:48:12Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/492#issuecomment-156144957",
